General.Name: Kollect on Demand Holding Ab
General.Description: Kollect on Demand Holding AB (publ), through its subsidiaries, offers waste management services in Ireland and the United Kingdom. The company offers domestic and commercial waste collection services; container rental services; and junk removal services for items, such as furniture, mattresses, and other large objects. It also operates an online platform for booking of waste collection services. In addition, the company provides BIGbin, a compactor bin for the disposal of domestic waste. Kollect on Demand Holding AB (publ) was incorporated in 2019 and is headquartered in Waterford, Ireland.
